_sText:
First Attempt Of Making A Jailbreak Map. If It Sucks Ass, I Am Sorry.

This is a very basic Jailbreak map. There is no disco / mini game or anything. There is a bare-bones Soccer field and a basic pool. Of course, there are secrets to help the Rebels achieve their malicious goals for killing the CTs. Some are obvious. I originally started this as a practice map, but it grew to be a Jailbreak map. 

If You Have Any Concerns Add Me On Steam.
